'''六氟磷酸锂''' 是一种[[无机化合物|无机化合物]] ，化学式 [[锂|Li]][[六氟磷酸盐|PF<sub>6</sub>]]。它是一种白色晶体粉末。 它用于商用二次电池，该应用利用了其在非水性极性[[溶剂|溶剂]]中的高溶解度。 具体地说，六氟磷酸锂在[[碳酸乙烯酯|碳酸乙烯酯]]，[[碳酸二甲酯|碳酸二甲酯]]，[[碳酸二乙酯|碳酸二乙酯]]和/或[[碳酸乙基甲基酯|碳酸乙基甲基酯]]的碳酸盐混合物中的溶液，其中含有少量的一种或多种添加剂[[氟代碳酸乙烯酯|氟代碳酸乙烯酯]]和{{le|碳酸亚乙烯酯|Vinylene carbonate}}等里作为[[锂离子电池|锂离子电池]]的最先进的[[电解质|电解质]]。 <ref>{{cite journal|last1=Goodenough|first1=John B.|last2=Kim|first2=Youngsik|title=Challenges for Rechargeable Li Batteries|journal=Chemistry of Materials|date=9 February 2010|volume=22|issue=3|pages=587–603|doi=10.1021/cm901452z}}</ref><ref name="QianHu2019">{{cite journal|last1=Qian|first1=Yunxian|last2=Hu|first2=Shiguang|last3=Zou|first3=Xianshuai|last4=Deng|first4=Zhaohui|last5=Xu|first5=Yuqun|last6=Cao|first6=Zongze|last7=Kang|first7=Yuanyuan|last8=Deng|first8=Yuanfu|last9=Shi|first9=Qiao|last10=Xu|first10=Kang|last11=Deng|first11=Yonghong|title=How electrolyte additives work in Li-ion batteries|journal=Energy Storage Materials|volume=20|year=2019|pages=208–215|issn=24058297|doi=10.1016/j.ensm.2018.11.015}}</ref> 该用处还利用了六氟磷酸根阴离子对强还原剂（例如锂金属）的惰性。

这个盐是对热稳定的， 不过在200 °C (392 °F) 下会损失一半的重量。它在接近70 °C (158 °F)下会水解<ref>{{cite journal|last1=Xu|first1=Kang|title=Nonaqueous Liquid Electrolytes for Lithium-Based Rechargeable Batteries|journal=Chemical Reviews|date=October 2004|volume=104|issue=10|pages=4303–4418|doi=10.1021/cr030203g|pmid=15669157|url=https://semanticscholar.org/paper/ba223d6006a7fcd52823f5c864a3307fa3d11c37|access-date=2020-09-20|archive-date=2021-03-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210302091838/https://www.semanticscholar.org/paper/Nonaqueous-liquid-electrolytes-for-lithium-based-Xu/ba223d6006a7fcd52823f5c864a3307fa3d11c37}}</ref> ，以以下反应形成剧毒的 HF 气体：
:LiPF<sub>6</sub>  +  H<sub>2</sub>O   →    HF  +  PF<sub>5</sub>  +  LiOH

由于Li<sup>+</sup>离子的[[路易斯酸|路易斯酸]]性质，LiPF<sub>6</sub>也会[[催化|催化]][[叔醇|叔醇]]的[[四氢吡喃|四氢吡喃]]反应。 <ref>{{cite journal | doi = 10.1055/s-2004-829550 | title = Lithium Hexafluorophosphate-Catalyzed Efficient Tetrahydropyranylation of Tertiary Alcohols under Mild Reaction Conditions | year = 2004 |author1=Nao Hamada|author2=Sato Tsuneo  | journal = Synlett | pages = 1802–1804 | issue = 10}}</ref>

在 [[锂离子电池|锂离子电池]]里，LiPF<sub>6</sub> 会和 Li<sub>2</sub>CO<sub>3</sub>反应，可被少量 HF催化： <ref name="BiWang2016">{{cite journal|last1=Bi|first1=Yujing|last2=Wang|first2=Tao|last3=Liu|first3=Meng|last4=Du|first4=Rui|last5=Yang|first5=Wenchao|last6=Liu|first6=Zixuan|last7=Peng|first7=Zhe|last8=Liu|first8=Yang|last9=Wang|first9=Deyu|last10=Sun|first10=Xueliang|title=Stability of Li2CO3 in cathode of lithium ion battery and its influence on electrochemical performance|journal=RSC Advances|volume=6|issue=23|year=2016|pages=19233–19237|issn=2046-2069|doi=10.1039/C6RA00648E}}</ref>

:LiPF<sub>6</sub>  +  Li<sub>2</sub>CO<sub>3</sub>   →    POF<sub>3</sub> + CO<sub>2</sub> + 3 LiF

